AboutMe.Title: About me
AboutMe.Paragraphs: I specialize in the framework Angular.
I work writing unit tests, performing continuous integration, and also covering backend developer roles with Spring Boot and MySQL.
My capabilities also include implementing improvements in systems, optimizing sites, standardizing patterns, and suggesting and executing ideas that add value to the project I am working on.
I am the sum of many skills and talents. I enjoy observing those who think disruptively and step out of their comfort zone.
I define myself not by the work I have done but by what I want to do. I can learn any skill. My way of being is what sets me apart from others.

I have ease in communication to understand, analyze, and provide solutions to client requirements.
I work comfortably autonomously but even more so doing it as a team and under agile methodology.
